relation: Darrow2 - #83 With raw power on his side, Giygas hopes to best Ness and Jeff, but once again proves to be too weak. Psh, embodiment of evil? More like embodiment of gettin' whupped.
Darrow2 - #84 As it would turn out, the next evolution in the Mani Mani battle isn't quite as weak as the others. A much more dangerous, menacing form bursts onto the battle and prepares to attack.
Darrow2 - #85 Caught in a death grip, Jeff is nearly crushed by Giygas, who has suddenly become a lot more powerful than previously indicated.
Darrow2 - #86 A few harsh words is all it takes to bring Giygas to the breaking point and finally, at long last, we see his true self appear.
Darrow2 - #87 The Universal Cosmic Destroyer emerges at last. The madness is no longer containable, nor is there any escape from it.
